&lt;p>&lt;a href="https://burgenland.orf.at/magazin/stories/3082537/" rel="noopener" target="_blank">Mahlzeit Burgenland: Christine Bauer und Krautfleckerl (in German)&lt;/a>&lt;/p>
&lt;p>Currently the radio program is also available as &lt;a href="https://static.orf.at/podcast/bgldmagazin/ORF_Burgenland_Mahlzeit_Burgenland.xml" rel="noopener" target="_blank">podcast&lt;/a>.&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>Video of my interview for LIWEST Kundenmagazin is online</title><link>https://chbeu.github.io/post/_posts_wordpress/2020-08-23-video-of-my-interview-for-liwest-kundenmagazin-is-online/</link><pubDate>Sun, 23 Aug 2020 14:43:32 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://chbeu.github.io/post/_posts_wordpress/2020-08-23-video-of-my-interview-for-liwest-kundenmagazin-is-online/</guid><description>&lt;p>My interview for LIWEST Kundenmagazin, Ausgabe Juli 2020 (&lt;a href="https://www.liwest.at/uploads/tx_liwestblaetterkatalog/LIWEST-Kundenmagazin_02_2020_web.pdf" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">[pdf]&lt;/a> &lt;a href="https://issuu.com/liwest_admin/docs/liwest-kundenmagazin_02_2020_web" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">[e-paper]&lt;/a>) was recorded.&lt;/p>
&lt;p>A 10 minutes cut of this interview is now online as a video at &lt;a href="https://www.dorftv.at/video/34030" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">dorf tv&lt;/a>.&lt;/p>
&lt;p>&lt;video controls>&lt;source src="https://www.dorftv.at/system/files/webvideos/x264_mid/34030.mp4" type="video/mp4">Your browser does not support the video tag.&lt;/video>&lt;/p>
&lt;p>Cooperation of LIWEST und dorf tv. Topic: Wie wissen Online-Plattformen wie Spotify &amp;amp; Co, welche Musik ihren Nutzern gefällt? (How do online platforms such as Spotify know what music its users like?). Interviewer: Christian Naderer. Camera and cut: Roland Freinschlag.&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>I am featured in the cover story of LIWEST Kundenmagazin</title><link>https://chbeu.github.io/post/_posts_wordpress/2020-07-24-i-am-featured-in-the-cover-story-of-liwest-kundenmagazin/</link><pubDate>Fri, 24 Jul 2020 19:05:43 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://chbeu.github.io/post/_posts_wordpress/2020-07-24-i-am-featured-in-the-cover-story-of-liwest-kundenmagazin/</guid><description>&lt;p>I gave an interview for the cover story of LIWEST Kundenmagazin (Ausgabe Juli 2020).&lt;/p>
&lt;p>We talked about my research on music recommender systems, but also about music streaming in general. And some private remarks ;-)&lt;/p>
