I am among the experts interviewed for this program which is broadcasted throughout the week. I will appear in part 2 (Tuesday) and 4 (Thursday).&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>We had some nice media presence lately</title><link>https://chbeu.github.io/post/_posts_wordpress/2019-07-08-we-had-some-nice-media-presence-recently/</link><pubDate>Mon, 08 Jul 2019 08:19:58 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://chbeu.github.io/post/_posts_wordpress/2019-07-08-we-had-some-nice-media-presence-recently/</guid><description>&lt;p>It&amp;rsquo;s great to see our scientific results being communicated to the public. Our results were well received on the media.&lt;/p>
