&lt;/ol>
&lt;p>And, well, also read the original &lt;a href="https://doi.org/10.1371/journal.pone.0217389" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">PLOS ONE article (open access) on music preferences in 47 countries with respect to what is considered mainstream including recommendation approaches considering users&amp;rsquo; mainstreaminess&lt;/a> by &lt;a href="http://www.mschedl.eu" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">Markus Schedl&lt;/a> and me.&lt;/p>
